sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Customer
  participant App as Spark City Wallet
  participant CE as Context Engine
  participant G as Local Graph
  participant AI as Gemma / Hermes + Gemini
  participant API as City Wallet API
  participant M as Merchant Checkout

  C->>App: Opens map or asks Spark
  App->>CE: Request current context
  CE->>CE: Combine location, time, weather, places, events, demand
  CE-->>App: Composite context + source evidence
  App->>G: Read local graph memory
  G-->>App: Preferences, routines, places, outcomes
  App->>AI: Private intent locally or abstract intent to Hermes
  AI-->>App: Grounded deal intelligence
  App->>API: Generate offer with context, rule, and insight
  API-->>App: Offer card with discount, expiry, reason, channel
  C->>App: Accepts offer
  App->>API: Issue redemption token
  API-->>App: QR token + proof
  C->>M: Presents QR
  M->>API: Validate token
  API-->>M: Validation result
  API-->>App: Ledger and analytics update
  App->>G: Record accepted/redeemed outcome locally
